data.description: This home is a must see! This stunning home features three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a very spacious living space that flows right into an updated kitchen. This kitchen boasts new countertops and backsplash that elevates the entire space! The covered patio provides great space for outdoor entertaining. Solar screens have been added to the windows to help block out this Texas heat. Located less than 5 minutes from I-30, you'll be near shopping and restaurants! Come by and see this one before it's gone!!
